      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "POTATO CAKES (6) turned in a plain effort last time when eighth at Shepparton over 450m behind Immobiliser (26.76) in a Maiden FIN. Was in the money the start prior. The form from his last run stacks up well. Tough to beat if on-song. QUENA LULLABY (7) slotted in just off the lead from the wide draw last start and boxed on to finish third (24.56) at this track in a Restricted WIN over 425m. Hard to beat again. ARAIZA (2) chased the lead early from the inside and boxed on well to finish second, beaten 1.75 lengths (24.74) at this track in a Bottom Up - Maiden over 425m. Expected to be in the finish again. UNLEASH GABBI (1) is a maiden but regularly finds a top-three finish.",
